SUMMARY:Columbus 3D Printer Review - ND2-40
LOCATION:"ND2-40"
DESCRIPTION:Hello\,\n\nThis meeting has been scheduled to review the 3D p
 rinters you observed during your tour at Ohio State. If you have any phot
 os you’d like displayed during the discussion\, please send them to me in
  advance. Including a label with the type of printer shown in each photo 
 would be especially helpful.\n\nRequired attendees include those who trav
 eled to Columbus for the site visit. All others are welcome to join if th
 ey would like to participate in the conversation.\n\nThank you\,\nColleen
 \n
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
